<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com/" crossorigin />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      as="style"
      onload="this.rel='stylesheet'"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?display=swap&family=Inter:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;700;900"
    />
    <title>About Us - ShortenIt</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="data:image/x-icon;base64," />
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("partials/navbar") %>

    <div class="px-40 flex flex-1 justify-center py-10 bg-[#121b26] min-h-screen">
      <div class="layout-content-container flex flex-col max-w-[960px] flex-1 text-white">
        <div class="@container">
          <h1
            class="text-[40px] font-black tracking-tight mb-6 @[480px]:text-5xl"
          >
            About Us
          </h1>
          <p class="text-base font-normal text-[#9cabba] leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-[720px]">
            ShortenIt is a leading link management platform dedicated to helping
            businesses and individuals effortlessly shorten, brand, and track
            their URLs. Our mission is to empower users with simple,
            yet powerful tools to enhance their online presence and marketing
            strategies.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base font-normal text-[#9cabba] leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-[720px]">
            Our platform was built with the vision of connecting people through
            better link management. We offer intuitive features including custom
            branded links, real-time click tracking, and in-depth analytics to
            help you understand your audience and optimize your campaigns.
          </p>

          <p class="text-base font-normal text-[#9cabba] leading-relaxed max-w-[720px]">
            At ShortenIt, security and reliability are our top priorities.
            We maintain a robust infrastructure to ensure your links are safe,
            fast, and always available. Our dedicated team is constantly
            innovating to bring you new features and improvements.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    
  </body>
